## **12. Security & Ethical Considerations**

* OAuth-based authentication
* No sensitive personal data stored
* Analytics tied only to User ID
* No punitive scoring or dark patterns

---

## **13. Scalability Considerations**

* Domain-agnostic data models
* JSON-based analytics allow schema evolution
* AI logic layer can later be replaced with ML models
* UI supports unlimited domains

---

## **14. Why This Tech Stack Wins Hackathons**

* Clean separation of concerns
* Demonstrates real AI system thinking
* Feels production-ready
* Easy to explain to judges
